3. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes an attention-based model that learns sentiment with respect to image-caption data, which is a machine learning approach. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper involves developing a model that can generate captions with sentiment, which is an application of artificial intelligence. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval): The paper may involve information retrieval techniques to retrieve relevant image-caption data for sentiment analysis.
